Package: getPNCT
Title: Download PNCT traffic data from DNIT
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Matheus", "Siqueira", , "matheusfsiqueira@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3341-0527"))
Description: getPNCT is an R wrapper for getting traffic data and other information from the PNCT Web API. It allows you to easily retrieve information on count sites, Annual Traffic, Monthly Traffic and Hourly Traffic.
